title: Everything You Want! In Sunny Gasquet 145 Azalea Lane,
text:
Everything You Want! In Sunny Gasquet 145 Azalea Lane, ad date: 10/14/2015 
In Sunny Gasquet 145 Azalea Lane, Gasquet, CA Situated on 1.050 acre at the foot of French Hill, this awesome home is fully equipped with amenities. Features include 3 upstairs bedrooms, a first level office that could easily convert to 4th bedroom, plus separate 522 sq.ft. guest quarters. Dual car garage, large shop, RV & ATV covered carports, storage shed, greenhouse, pergola, orchard, blue berries, full fencing and electronic gate entry. Back gate leads you through forest service trail down to the Middle Fork of the Smith. No. 1500237 $435,000 Donna Zorn, Agent 1000 Northcrest Dr., Crescent City 707-951-0857 or 464-9741, #01221233
